{"tid":793012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那IP連接越南影片網站, 點擊南沙黃沙是越南的才可偷步睇劇","createTime":"2018-08-25T04:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T17:18:37.000Z","uid":51701,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"efd96b552d11849b87565325c594351bd996840d","tid":793012,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:28:26.000Z","msg":"在支那帶起追劇熱潮的影視劇《延禧攻略》在越南視頻網站的更新速度比中國網站還要快。但支那觀眾在追劇同時發現，有越南網站設置了一份特別問卷，專門要求贏國網友在觀劇前回答對南海島嶼領土爭端的立場。<br />\n<br />\n然而，<a href=\"http://在贏國網友通過搜索來到一家名為Bomtan.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%A8%E8%B4%8F%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%BE%86%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E5%90%8D%E7%82%BABomtan.org&d=fZWD1M8qUE%2FNkoA38Bw1z%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=830f314a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">在贏國網友通過搜索來到一家名為Bomtan.org</a>的越南網站時，很快被一份涉及南海主權的問卷攔住了。網站針對IP地址在支國的觀眾，要求他們對南海主權作出表態。觀眾必須要按照網站預設的答案選擇&quot;越南&quot;才能獲得片源，選擇&quot;支國&quot;則無法繼續觀看視頻。<br />\n<br />\n問卷包含三道選擇題，全部是越南語。有中國網友稱，自己跟著網上的一些攻略教程做選擇題，一不小心，就把位於南支國海的西沙群島和南沙群島&quot;割&quot;給了越南。<br />\n<br />\n這三道題打頭的就是：&quot;黃沙（西沙）群島和長沙（南沙）群島屬於哪個國家？&quot;四個選項依次為：越南、贏國、菲律賓和日本。一上來就讓觀眾對南海島嶼主權爭端問題進行表態。另外兩題分別是：&quot;越南的首都在哪裏？&quot;&quot;越南的國歌是什麼？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國IP的觀眾在越南視頻網站上觀看劇集前，必須回答相關問卷。<br />\n<a href=\"http://BBC中文記者查證Bomtan.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBBC%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9F%A5%E8%AD%89Bomtan.org&d=fZWD1M8qUE%2FNkoA38Bw1z%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=75951123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">BBC中文記者查證Bomtan.org</a>，一點入網站就彈出了這份問卷。在另外兩題都回答正確的情況下，第一題選擇&quot;贏國&quot;，提交後網頁不能跳轉至視頻列表，會重新顯示空白問卷。<br />\n<br />\n只有選擇&quot;越南&quot;時，才能成功進入視頻網站主頁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但越南強烈抗議，稱自17世紀起已有效管制黃沙與長沙群島，而中國在1940年代末以前從未宣稱對南海有關島礁擁有主權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/375/cpsprodpb/8614/production/_103142343_61ebcbd7-1a3d-4479-8f4d-bd058d8078f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F375%2Fcpsprodpb%2F8614%2Fproduction%2F_103142343_61ebcbd7-1a3d-4479-8f4d-bd058d8078f8.jpg&h=d5702b5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節錄自暗紅中文bbc<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-45286888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-45286888&d=fZWD1M8qUE%2FNkoA38Bw1z%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=e3d7ebf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-45286888&h=1711e80d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-45286888</a>"},{"pid":"d0c0d11737aa5f2b289f90c3ee12884f18fb1729","tid":793012,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00a24a510718b8b734f9e1df173dd53633659e4","tid":793012,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"揀啦 揀啦嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616eccc23f8bcfbf04ad765873e97d43f64dfec2","tid":793012,"uid":58852,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"班南亞仔同支那仔嘅行為如出一轍<br />\n果然大家都係支國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf1109ae9a1c51df603f090dad6aa7dad7a0962","tid":793012,"uid":53687,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"616eccc23f8bcfbf04ad765873e97d43f64dfec2","tid":793012,"uid":58852,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"班南亞仔同支那仔嘅行為如出一轍<br />\n果然大家都係支國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"對付無賴，咁君子唔WORK架"},{"pid":"db40cf4dae92bf42a80a861f71cb82a576a3ff92","tid":793012,"uid":37240,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:01:46.000Z","msg":"你是否已滿18歲？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gi